apiDescription: This object allows users to check the spelling of Comments and Form Fields and other spelling domains. To be able to use the `spell` object, the user must have installed the Acrobat Spelling plug-in and the spelling dictionaries. !! Note The `spell` object is not available in versions of Adobe Reader prior to 7.0. In Adobe Reader 7.0, all properties and methods—with the exception of `customDictionaryCreate` , `customDictionaryDelete` and `customDictionaryExport` —are accessible.
